112				Result: req.A * req.B,
113			}, nil
114		}
115	
116		multiplyTool, err := tools.SafeInferTool("multiply", "multiply two numbers", multiply)
117		if err != nil {
118			return nil, err
119		}
120	
121		type divideReq struct {
122			A float64 `json:"a"`
123			B float64 `json:"b"`
124		}
125	
126		type divideResp struct {
127			Result float64
128		}
129	
130		divide := func(ctx context.Context, req *divideReq) (*divideResp, error) {
131			return &divideResp{
132				Result: req.A / req.B,
133			}, nil
134		}
135	
136		divideTool, err := tools.SafeInferTool("divide", "divide two numbers", divide)
137		if err != nil {
138			return nil, err
139		}
140		return adk.NewChatModelAgent(ctx, &adk.ChatModelAgentConfig{
141			Name:        "math_agent",
142			Description: "the agent responsible to do math",
143			Instruction: `
144			You are a math agent.
145	
146	
147	        INSTRUCTIONS:
148	        - Assist ONLY with math-related tasks
149	        - After you're done with your tasks, respond to the supervisor directly
150	        - Respond ONLY with the results of your work, do NOT include ANY other text.`,
151			Model: m,
152			ToolsConfig: adk.ToolsConfig{
153				ToolsNodeConfig: compose.ToolsNodeConfig{
154					Tools: []tool.BaseTool{addTool, multiplyTool, divideTool},
155					UnknownToolsHandler: func(ctx context.Context, name, input string) (string, error) {
156						return fmt.Sprintf("unknown tool: %s", name), nil
157					},
158				},
159			},
160		})
161	}
162	
163	func buildSupervisor(ctx context.Context) (adk.Agent, error) {
164		m := model.NewChatModel()
165	
166		sv, err := adk.NewChatModelAgent(ctx, &adk.ChatModelAgentConfig{
167			Name:        "supervisor",
168			Description: "the agent responsible to supervise tasks",
169			Instruction: `
170			You are a supervisor managing two agents:
171	
172	        - a research agent. Assign research-related tasks to this agent
173	        - a math agent. Assign math-related tasks to this agent
174	        Assign work to one agent at a time, do not call agents in parallel.
175	        Do not do any work yourself.`,
176			Model: m,
177			Exit:  &adk.ExitTool{},
178		})
179		if err != nil {
180			return nil, err
181		}
182	
183		searchAgent, err := buildSearchAgent(ctx)
184		if err != nil {
185			return nil, err
186		}
187		mathAgent, err := buildMathAgent(ctx)
188		if err != nil {
189			return nil, err
190		}
191	
192		return supervisor.New(ctx, &supervisor.Config{
193			Supervisor: sv,
194			SubAgents:  []adk.Agent{searchAgent, mathAgent},
195		})
196	}
